Preconditions:
The `beginWord` and `endWord` parameters should not be null.
The `wordDict` parameter should not be null.
The `wordDict` parameter should contain at least one word.
The length of `beginWord` and `endWord` should be the same.
The `beginWord` and `endWord` should be present in the `wordDict` list.

Postconditions:
The method should return an integer value representing the number of words in the shortest transformation sequence from `beginWord` to `endWord`.
If no such sequence exists, the method should return 0.